43256576, \"rank\": 0.09755120662899412, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/World Rugby  China beat Kenya 24-7 in the women's final at the World Rugby Sevens Repechage in Monaco on Sunday, securing qualification for the event at the upcoming 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5655366551636454, \"rank\": 0.768149732252457, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.99989619250148, \"rank\": 9.032665412036824e-05, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\", \"score\": 0.9999999462320389, \"rank\": 5.376795389534735e-08, \"text\": \"World Rugby\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9110397443256576, \"rank\": 0.09755120662899412, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999513281649, \"rank\": 4.867181606612854e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese national team won all six of their games at the tournament in dominant fashion, including defeating Paraguay 31-0 and walking over Poland 40-7 in the knockout round to advance to the final.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9687048740064081, \"rank\": 0.027894993278076027, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 753, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999990080530469, \"rank\": 9.905579015486228e-07, \"text\": \"Paraguay\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999935267881358, \"rank\": 5.331544355062182e-06, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are feeling really good, we are so excited to go to Paris,\\\" China's Chen Keyi said.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999513281649, \"rank\": 4.867181606612854e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 908, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5655366551636454, \"rank\": 0.768149732252457, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Keyi\", \"score\": 0.9999946898451544, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Keyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Keyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Keyi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we deserve it, we work so hard for each other, on and off the field.\\\"\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are so proud of ourselves; we are so proud of our teammates; and we are so proud of our coaches,\\\" Chen's teammate Liu Xiaoqian added.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"score\": 0.9637163376060651, \"rank\": 0.019112284826618794, \"text\": \"Chen\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shui-bian\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Xiaoqian_(rugby_union)\", \"score\": 0.7999903763666297, \"rank\": 0.24999999999997063, \"text\": \"Liu Xiaoqian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Xiaoqian_(rugby_union)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Xiaoqian_(rugby_union)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa clinched qualification for the Paris Olympics on the men's side after overcoming Great Britain 14-5 in the final.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.999999988546506, \"rank\": 1.047480694525267e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a pretty special group we have here, just to cherish the moment is what we are living for,\\\" South Africa's Tristan Leyds told reporters.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"score\": 0.999999988546506, \"rank\": 1.047480694525267e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa_national_rugby_sevens_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"score\": 0.9856658060328497, \"rank\": 0.010265116503535525, \"text\": \"Tristan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tristan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of external pressure, the people back home get disappointed [when we do not perform], but we kept the group tight and it paid off, we qualified for Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999513281649, \"rank\": 4.867181606612854e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have some pretty special youngsters in our team, they made us proud this week,\\\" Leyds' teammate Rosko Specman added.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"score\": 0.9999997995160103, \"rank\": 1.5980226695534914e-07, \"text\": \"Rosko\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rosko\"}, {\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"score\": 0.8020135056823948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Specman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Specman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[The Olympics] is the biggest sporting event in the world.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's pretty special to play in an Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": []}]}"